      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>I know they love me, but love doesn't make the medical bills go away or fixing my mistakes any easier. It feels selfish to keep dragging them into my decline. I've always been the one taking care of everyone... now that I'm the one who needs care, it just feels wrong. Like I'm breaking the natural order of things. It would be so much simpler for them if they didn't have to worry about me anymore.",
